summary: Stump Cottage is a follower friendly unique little home next to Falkreath.
descriptionHtml:
Stump Cottage is a fully navmeshed, unique player home next to Falkreath. It's basically a house in a giant tree stump. Has three unowned beds, cooking, oven, alchemy table, enchanter, a Shrine of Julianos and several containers, all of them are safe. Perfect for a character who wants to live close to the nature. Requires all DLCs.
Thanks to izon97604 for featuring my mod in a youtube review (the video is in the comments). :)
author: FarrinRacer
